It provides type annotations for the `aiobotocore.SageMaker` service, compatible with various IDEs and tools like VSCode, PyCharm, and mypy. The package, generated with `mypy-boto3-builder 7.23.2`, aims to enhance code quality by enabling type checking and code completion. It includes features like client, paginator, and waiter annotations, along with literals and type definitions for comprehensive type checking.
